ess ActorSystem/Props/serialization/configuration testing.\",\n  \"deterministic_setup\": [],\n  \"agent_guidance\": \"Use APIs present in Pekko 2.0.0-M1. Do not reuse the old 1.1.5 TypedActor/TypedProps tests: Pekko 2.0 removes many deprecated APIs and the 2.0.0-M1 jar no longer contains org.apache.pekko.actor.TypedActor, TypedActorExtension, or TypedProps. Prefer classic actor APIs from pekko-actor itself, such as ActorSystem, Props, ActorRef, dispatchers, DynamicAccess, SerializationExtension, and ConfigFactory-backed configuration. Only retain the existing java.base/sun.net.dns add-exports if tests intentionally exercise DNS internals.\",\n  \"risks\": [\n    \"The observed failure is caused by stale tests targeting removed Pekko 1.x TypedActor APIs, not by missing setup.\",\n    \"Pekko documentation lists pekko-testkit as a test dependency for conventional Pekko application tests, but it is not required to reach meaningful coverage of the pekko-actor artifact in this TCK scaffold.\",\n    \"Do not add separate Pekko modules such as pekko-actor-typed, pekko-remote, or persistence-related artifacts unless the generated tests intentionally switch scope to those artifacts; they are not required for the requested library.\"\n  ]\n}", "textSignature": "{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_06b0bcc517273e32016a420039bd688196a41bfc979e9d45f8\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "oca/gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 1574, "output": 873, "cacheRead": 24064, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 26511, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "stop", "timestamp": 1782710319424, "responseId": "resp_06b0bcc517273e32016a42002feae48196803c7c8c03f8eb02"}, "toolResults": []}
